**Loan prepayment** (part-prepayment) is paying an amount over and above your regular EMI to reduce your outstanding principal. This reduces both the total interest payable and the remaining loan tenure. For a ₹50 lakh home loan at 8.5%, a single prepayment of ₹5 lakh in Year 3 can save over ₹8 lakh in interest and reduce tenure by 2+ years.
